 The site also serves as a simple way of <span class="th">exchanging ideas</span> with acquainted musicians.<br>
  Under <span class="th">Vita and Repertoire</span> I briefly describe my musical development
 and my idea and conception of making music.
 Under </span>Audio</span> you will find recordings of my music, grouped by category.
 In the <span class="th">video section</span> you will find musical impressions that have had an influence on my style.
 The <span class="th">repertoire</span> includes original compositions, interpretations and original literature.
 Under <span class="th">Live Sets</span> you can see my current concert programs with a detailed song list.
 In the <span class="th">Gear section</span> you will find a detailed overview with pictures and thoughts
 about my instruments and equipment.
